 from  to  and averaging about  it operates in arizona california delaware florida georgia illinois kentucky maryland michigan minnesota new jersey new york north carolina ohio pennsylvania south carolina texas virginia washington dc and west virginia members of the hovnanian family including ara k hovnanian have voting control over approximately  of the votes as of october   equivalent to a stake worth  million in  the company relocated its corporate headquarters to a new building on the banks of the navesink river in red bank new jersey in  historyedit in  kevork hovnanian an ethnic armenian originally from iraq and his three brothers  hirair hovnanian jirair hovnanian and vahak hovananian  each contributed  dollars in addition to  which they borrowed to found hovnanian enterprises inc in a trailer in toms river new jersey hovnanian and his company earned a reputation to selling low cost condos and townhouses many to first time young homeowners and families a typical twobedroom two bathroom hovnanian home built in the early s cost approximately  because hovnanian eliminated amenities such as communal swimming pools which other builders used to attract potential buyers in a new york times interview in  hovnanian explained his reasoning for marketing low cost homes in developments without community amenities there are limited recreation facilities going in because people have little time for socialization in  jirair hovnanian split off from his brothers company and founded his own construction business js hovnanian  sons of mount laurel township new jersey hirair and vahak also left the company by  to found their own enterprises hovnanian enterprises had built and sold more than  homes and condos by  an additional  residences were sold between  and  as the company expanded its construction to include luxury homes midpriced homes and retirement communities it remains one the united states largest builders of active adult homes which are sold under the name of four seasons communities kevork hovnanian stepped down as president of hovnanian enterprises in  and was succeeded by his son ara k hovnanian he remained chief executive until his retirement in  and was also replaced as ceo by ara hovnanian however he remained the chairman of the companys board of directors until his death in  ara hovnanian is a graduate of the university of pennsylvania wharton school and led the company through  acquisitions of smaller builders from  through the early stages of the housing crisis the company relied heavily on debt to fund the acquisitions however falling property prices has forced the company to write off more than  billion of its value since  as of october  the companys debt load is  billion and interest payments amount to  million to  million per quarter qualityedit hovnanian has been the subject of customer complaints in a few cases there have been legitimate construction problems in some hovnanian houses for example in  hovnanian acknowledged problems in a development in new jersey after nearly three dozen disgruntled homeowners turned to elected officials when their complaints were ignored k hovnanian the home builder and the mortgage company are no strangers to controversy in  the home builder was involved in a class action lawsuit where the plaintiffs alleged their subdivision was built near an old bombing range the company settled the lawsuit in  for a reported  million source httpthemortgageinsidernetmortgagereviewskhovnanianamericanmortgagereviewhtml the mortgage company was involved in a class action lawsuit filed in  alleging violations of the real estate settlement procedures act respa for removing incentives from home buyers if they opted to use another title insurance provider rather than the hovnanianaffiliated title insurance company source httpthemortgageinsidernetmortgagereviewskhovnanianamericanmortgagereviewhtml k hovnanian homes has also been the subject of praise from homeowners citing the builders reputation and solid history hovnanian has also received numerous awards based on the quality of their construction and high level customer support external linksedit k hovnanian homes corporate website k hovnanian american mortgage llc  financial services yahoo  hovnanian enterprises inc company profile kevork and ara hovnanian hovnanian enterprises inc reuters company profile for hov hovnanian enterprises referencesedit  a b c d e f g h hovnanian enterprises inc  annual report  form k  december   pdf secdatabasecom retrieved    a b c willis david p  homebuilder leaves legacy of philanthropy asbury park press archived from the original on  retrieved    httpwwwinvestorreuterswallstcomstockscompanyprofileasprpctickerhov  a b c d e f g h i j meier barry  kevork s hovnanian construction company founder dies at  the new york times retrieved    sims gayle nonan  js hovnanian new jersey builder dies the philadelphia inquirer retrieved  dead link  hudson kris debt load hinders recovery at hovnanian wall street journal issn  retrieved    nj state report details homebuilding flaws daily real estate news realtor magazine online march     woman trades noisy neighbor for a peaceful k hovnanian home asbury park press appcom january   accessed february    k hovnanian homes earns national housing quality certification for outstanding quality assurance and customer satisfaction nahb research center nahbrcorg september   accessed february    six quality methods for award winning performance of national housing quality award winners toolbase services toolbaseorg accessed february   retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlehovnanianenterprisesoldid categories companies established in home buildersconstruction and civil engineering companies of the united statescompanies listed on the new york stock exchangecompanies based in monmouth county new jerseyred bank new jersey establishments in new jerseyhidden categories all articles with dead external linksarticles with dead external links from oct